        "method": "Sampling-based movement with heuristic upgrade scoring",
        "description": "Each tick, score 97 candidate movements (48 boss-mode + 32 wave-mode + 16 half-speed, plus stay-still). Score each candidate by: bullet trajectory danger (multi-step lookahead), enemy collision avoidance, boss alignment, item attraction, and ideal-position bias. Select the highest-scoring candidate. Upgrade picks use a text-keyword scoring function tuned with wave-conditional rules to avoid cascade breakage.",
        "key_design_decisions": [
          "SPEED=38 (just under speed_cap=40): fast enough to dodge aggressively without triggering cap",
          "dangerWeight=14000: empirically found value; \u00b130% causes cascade failures on different seeds",
          "Boss mode (48 dirs, 12 lookahead steps): more candidates for bullet-dense boss patterns",
          "Wave mode (32 dirs, 9 lookahead steps): fewer candidates but sufficient for wave enemies",
          "Lead targeting: predict boss X position accounting for boss velocity and wall bounces",
          "Stay 300px below boss: optimal shooting distance for auto-fire (bullet vel=[0,-8.5])",
          "Wave-conditional upgrade scoring: \u53d7\u5230\u4f24\u5bb3\u540e (thorn armor) excluded only in wave 3; \u6e05\u9664\u8109\u51b2/\u65e0\u575a\u4e0d\u6467 penalized only in wave 3; split bullets get +400 bonus in wave 3",
          "Anti-oscillation: detect variance<20 over 20 ticks and repel from recent positions",
          "Panic mode: 20 ticks of forced movement when shield drops >50 in one tick"
        ],
        "cascade_sensitivity": "The game is deterministic: any change to movement or upgrade scoring changes enemy kill timing \u2192 different XP drops \u2192 different level-up timing \u2192 completely different upgrade options. Even 3.5% change to dangerWeight breaks previously-winning seeds.",
